Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.44,0:01:27.15,lassie episode,,0,0,0,,{TIME:82440,87150}GOODBYE LASSIE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.81,0:01:31.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:88810,91900}Was its owner using this boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:36.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:91900,96990}That's because I found its leash in this boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:40.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:97430,100460}When I read the name written on it,\Nit replied immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:43.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:102270,103650}Isn't it, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.98,0:01:45.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:104980,105760}You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.55,0:01:49.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108550,109890}Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:51.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110160,111670}Oh, is it you, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.70,0:01:54.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111700,114590}Don't you know who owns that boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:01:55.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114610,115280}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:57.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:115610,117170}Ah, that one...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.17,0:02:01.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:117170,121250}That was here just a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.25,0:02:03.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:121250,123990}Maybe it has no owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.01,0:02:06.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125010,126330}I knew when I looked at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:13.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:126900,133070}The boat's rope was cut off, indicating\Nthat the owner was running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:13.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133090,133690}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:16.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133770,136260}Perhaps not to run away,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:18.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136300,138960}I think the rope it teared by itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:21.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:140070,141630}Maybe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:25.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141630,145110}In fact I don't know\Nthe answer to your question.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:39.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156320,159970}Where did this boat come from?\NI wish I could find the answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.78,0:02:44.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:160780,164130}Tell me, where did you came from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.47,0:02:50.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168470,170530}Is it wise to move it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:53.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170560,173850}But we must find the owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:54.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173870,174620}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.68,0:02:55.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174680,175710}Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:03.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180310,183750}Because, if we know where it came from
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:07.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184370,187160}we may find the mother of Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:08.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187540,188720}Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:12.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188870,192380}I understand, if you find the owner\Nyou will give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:13.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192380,193630}{\i1}We have no other choice!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:15.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194100,195810}We have no other choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:22.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195880,202520}True, if Lassie lives with its mother,\Nit will live happily ever after.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:25.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204020,205500}Maybe you are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:28.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207670,208890}It's an airplane!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:33.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209830,213160}{\i1}The delivery goods that were\Nin my house are on the plane now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.16,0:03:34.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213160,214450}{\i1}My father is a contractor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:41.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217630,221660}I remembered, I met you for the first time\Nwhen I saw the plane flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:47.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223750,227370}If the plane wasn't there,\NI would't meet Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:03.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242010,243810}This is the school road!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:06.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244620,246520}That bridge we always see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247600,249160}What?! John and Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:11.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249160,251150}Where did you get this boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:15.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254690,255740}Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.05,0:04:18.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256050,258980}We are going to Lassie's mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:19.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259050,259740}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:22.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259820,262010}Have you found the owner of the puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:22.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262040,262760}{\i1}Not yet!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:27.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264660,267420}But I'm sure we'll find Lassie's mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:31.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267420,271930}Wait for me! I'll go with you!\NWait! Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:34.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272520,274180}There is the backyard of the houses!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:35.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274180,275090}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.09,0:04:36.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275090,276930}First time I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:41.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279080,281140}I saw him, I saw him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:43.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283040,283920}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:47.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285980,287680}Mr. Curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:54.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292070,294460}She's so beautiful, teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:05:01.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298370,301370}The village looks quite different by the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:02.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301480,302140}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:12.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311050,312240}{\i1}Dr. Hooper!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:17.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313620,317650}Hello, you're Carraclough's son, isn't it?\NThat's a good boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:19.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318120,319500}Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:23.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320650,323720}This remainds me... what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:28.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324570,328900}I remembered, I saw a puppy on board\Nof this boat two or three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:31.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328900,331400}Dr. Hooper, have you seen it before?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:35.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331400,335490}Yes, it came on this river.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:36.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:335490,336060}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:36.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336060,336720}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:39.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337340,339500}Doctor, thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:45.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339810,345800}Hey, it's important not to tell\Nyour mother that you saw me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:56.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354910,356670}What is it? You are a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365050,366870}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:38.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397180,398580}We crossed a long distance...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.76,0:06:40.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398760,400670}How long we'll continue this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.41,0:06:42.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401410,402030}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:44.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403510,404830}{\i1}It's a steamer!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:06:58.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418140,418980}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:03.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421960,423160}Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:06.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425120,426080}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:09.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428710,429900}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.90,0:07:18.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436900,438210}This is dangerous, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:21.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438290,441610}If you cross this road, you will be crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:26.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444980,446320}What is it with this wheel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:27.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446320,447320}{\i1}John!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:28.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:447430,448470}{\i1}Hey John!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:31.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449630,451660}Look here! This rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:35.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452100,455440}It's the same rope as on the boat,\Nit's cut in the same shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:37.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455900,457550}Well that means...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:41.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457850,461070}Look, the two ropes are exactly the samel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:44.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461190,464350}So Lassie was coming from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:48.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464800,468170}We are going to find your mother soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:51.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:470440,471980}{\i1}We finally found her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:08:00.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478220,480630}Hey, it's so annoying, so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:04.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481050,484570}You two! Children, you are making\Nnoise around other people's houses!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:09.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486300,489870}Hey! It's my boat that I lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:10.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489920,490830}Eh... eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:17.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493220,497240}Well, we came to look for\Nthe owner of this boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:18.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497480,498690}It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:20.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:499550,500760}Whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:22.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501860,502640}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:24.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502930,504170}What's with this puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:27.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504190,507370}Sorry for this... sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:30.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508060,510070}Isn't that Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:30.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510090,510690}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:33.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512050,513040}This means...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:37.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514280,517150}Uncle, do you know anything about Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:40.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517530,520040}Of course I know, because it's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:41.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520590,521620}What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:44.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:522460,524410}Do you want to say this again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:47.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524480,527940}No, I understand, I will return it immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:49.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528710,529490}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.97,0:08:51.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529970,531070}What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:55.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531730,535170}It stayed with me for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.27,0:08:58.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535270,538370}after it almost crumbled\Nunder the feet of the sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:09:02.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538570,542000}So please let me say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:02.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542160,542860}Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544310,546770}I will give it some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:08.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546910,548230}When you finish it, bring it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:19.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:556650,559450}This is great, Lassie, we've found your owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:21.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560770,561700}{\i1}Lassie...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:24.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562410,564810}Give your mother a lot of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:27.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565090,567000}Take care of yourself, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:30.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567920,570310}I won't forget you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:36.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572720,576100}Come on, now go to your mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:45.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582450,585420}Hey go! Don't you want to meet your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:49.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589320,589870}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:53.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591300,593370}Lassie, not that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:02.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599480,602430}I understand, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:05.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602460,605000}I will do it immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:06.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605420,606570}Oh, the child!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:09.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606920,609790}{\i1}Don't play here, move right away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:11.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610200,611850}This is not a place to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:14.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612700,614750}I understand, I'll do it right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:19.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614750,619280}The water level must rise quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.15,0:10:24.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620150,624040}Shut up, our steam pump is not...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:28.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626420,628800}Damn, I have no time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:36.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635280,636840}Hey kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:40.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637360,640080}{\i1}Come here and help me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:49.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644060,649160}Listen Lassie, this is just a wheel,\Nso you have to go to your owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:49.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649350,649970}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:53.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:650130,653170}{\i1}So pull more and work hard, kid!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:59.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656550,659770}What is the matter? Can't you move it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:03.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:662770,663820}What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:06.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663820,666150}Close the gate to raise the water level!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:11.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667030,671230}This side must be closed\Nwhen this ship comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:15.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672150,675630}We must send the high water\Nto the opposite side!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:17.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675630,677410}What is the matter? Have you closed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:19.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678440,679390}It's closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:29.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686160,689340}But, why do you do that, Colin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:33.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:690440,693960}I did this because the uncle\Nasked me to do so, to use my force.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:35.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693960,695070}What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.08,0:11:38.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696080,698840}Kid, have you called this puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.26,0:11:59.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713260,719370}And as it looks, they can leave now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.50,0:12:03.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:722500,723970}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:05.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723970,725940}I still want to rest more...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:06.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:726070,726770}Pff...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:08.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727000,728080}You can't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:10.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728910,730750}Are you satisfied with this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:17.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:733060,737220}And don't you think of coming here again,\Ngo away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:21.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:738320,741290}Uncle, will you use it for guarding?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:24.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:741370,744150}Don't ask about things that don't concern you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:26.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744180,746430}{\i1}Do you live here alone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:27.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:746430,747380}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:30.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747380,750700}Don't you have a family other than this puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:32.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750700,752410}{\i1}What's wrong with that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:35.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754290,755930}If there is no other choice for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:41.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:759820,761310}Well get here immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:44.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762120,764280}{\i1}If you'll do bad things, I'll eat you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:49.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765970,769880}{\i1}You must open the rest of the gates quickly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.88,0:12:51.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:769880,771140}{\i1}Wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:21.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:797990,801950}I'm sure that man knows\Nhow to behave with the poor Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.08,0:13:23.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802080,803540}I hope so, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.64,0:13:26.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804640,806220}I found it, I should tell him so!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:27.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806250,807150}John?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:33.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811380,813820}What is it? You are the child\Nwho came earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:35.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814180,815300}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:36.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815480,816540}Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.22,0:13:40.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817220,820520}Lassie drinks milk from a child's bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:41.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820890,821990}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:44.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822930,824200}So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:48.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:824970,828410}But you try to train it to eat from the dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:49.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:828410,829310}So... sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:51.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829520,831700}You, uncle, will you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:54.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832490,834990}{\i1}How long will you keep bothering me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:59.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836310,839210}I have no time to train it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:02.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839580,842370}If it doesn't drink milk\Nby its own, is it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:05.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842400,845070}Is it over? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:08.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845300,848140}I don't know, how will I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.75,0:14:11.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849750,851570}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:15.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852130,855660}{\i1}Well, this world is not that easy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:16.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:855990,856800}John...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:17.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857100,857820}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:19.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858220,859780}Come on, let 's go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.43,0:14:25.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864430,865510}Eh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:29.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:866620,869950}Listen, John, let's go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:32.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:870410,872580}But that sounds fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:35.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873530,875500}Ah, it worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:56.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893850,896540}Don't look at my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:09.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905640,909230}What is it, why do you look\Nat other people's houses?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:11.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:909230,911250}But I was surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:14.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911520,914460}That an amazing machine like this\Ncould be found in someone's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:17.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914660,917350}Would you let me look at it a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:18.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917350,918590}I will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:21.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:919330,921270}I told you not to look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:22.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921270,922150}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:22.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922150,922990}What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:24.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922990,924370}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:26.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924830,926370}Don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.79,0:15:30.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:929790,930920}It's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:33.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931630,933300}Not here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:38.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935600,938120}You have to leave immediately, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:41.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:938410,941520}Sorry, is there a house for the dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:42.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941560,942240}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:44.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:942290,944680}A dog house? There is no such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:48.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944710,948710}Hey? No house for the dog?\NWhere did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.06,0:15:50.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949060,950800}{\i1}What do you want from me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.93,0:15:53.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950930,953320}I don't have time for your likes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:57.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956170,957230}Get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:58.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:957460,958890}I said no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:02.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958890,962000}What would you do if a ship\Npassed by and didn't notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:05.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962390,965450}Another question? Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:09.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966400,969030}Hey, listen to me, uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:12.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970120,972070}{\i1}I want to ask you something else!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.16,0:16:14.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972160,974070}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:15.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974170,975850}It's important!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.69,0:16:18.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976690,978480}John, enough, let 's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:20.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978510,980960}But... it's really important!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:26.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983000,986310}I will answer only one question!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:27.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986310,987230}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:32.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988520,992710}Excuse me, what do you have\Nto eat for today, uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.82,0:16:36.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994820,996400}How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:38.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996750,998670}Is this what you wanted to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:39.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998760,999680}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:43.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002810,1003790}It's canned food!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:44.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003790,1004800}Canned food?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:48.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004800,1008340}Yes, today canned food\Nand every day canned food!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.51,0:16:51.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008510,1011690}I don't have time to cook\Nso my food is just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:55.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013080,1015780}Hey, this is great...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:17:00.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016140,1020930}It's not like it's good, there's no food to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:07.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022140,1027300}Kid, why are you interested by my food?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:13.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027670,1033040}If you don't have food to eat,\Nyou may have to eat Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:14.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033130,1034000}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:18.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034330,1038100}If you think I'll really eat the puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:19.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038410,1039980}I can't eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.28,0:17:23.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041280,1043050}Maybe this is the truth but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:28.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043430,1048680}But I don't see Lassie's mother here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:29.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048930,1049640}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:32.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049720,1052100}You don't see Lassie's mother here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.10,0:17:34.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052100,1054110}Where is Lassie's mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:37.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054230,1057060}I didn't eat it, because I don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:41.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057720,1061250}Uncle! I don't see it! Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:46.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061950,1066870}I want to find Lassie's mother\Nand bring it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:49.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067360,1069650}Why isn't it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:52.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069930,1072670}The puppy's mother is really not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:54.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072670,1074910}Yes, I looked around the place thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:58.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074910,1078940}He's a liar! He's not the owner of Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:03.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081570,1083680}I'm not a liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:05.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083930,1085560}I hate lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:09.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087830,1089600}It's because of that driver!\NThe driver...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:14.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090540,1094080}Driver! Yes, that wheel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:18.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096690,1098190}Do you know that, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:22.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098190,1102520}No, but it was strange of Lassie\Nto smell that wheel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:27.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104120,1107690}{\i1}A few days ago there was\Na car on this road with a flat tire.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:32.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108570,1112050}{\i1}He is said he was coming from a foreign\Ncountry and was accompanied by a Collie dog.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:37.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112980,1117710}When the driver fix his car,\Nthis puppy fled away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.71,0:18:39.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117710,1119140}He couldn't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:42.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119810,1122810}The port was far away and\Nhe couldn't stay any longer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:44.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122810,1124360}so he decided to leave it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:49.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124810,1129350}He also asked me to take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.68,0:18:53.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129680,1133200}You understand, this puppy belongs to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.39,0:18:56.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133390,1136080}{\i1}He left it under my care,\Nso I have no other choice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:19:00.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138430,1140430}Stop with that bark!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:03.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140580,1143630}You can't take care of it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.11,0:19:07.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144110,1147520}You have to promise me\Nthat you will take good care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:09.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147520,1149690}Stupid, in such a place...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:13.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152060,1153370}What are you doing, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:17.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153400,1157160}I thought it would grow better with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:20.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157160,1160690}but if I left Lassie with you, it would die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:22.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160690,1162080}For sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:26.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162330,1166360}I mean you wanted to take care of it\Ninstead of someone like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.49,0:19:27.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166490,1167580}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:29.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167580,1169640}No? Don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:31.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169640,1171040}I'm not a liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.47,0:19:32.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171470,1172750}And now stay there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.42,0:19:36.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174420,1176910}You want to take care of it\Nuntil it grows up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.93,0:19:38.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176930,1178060}I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:41.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179440,1181510}You are a honest kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:46.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184620,1186470}He made me go and come with no reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:48.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186500,1188080}John, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:53.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191480,1193440}Well, don't come here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:57.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193440,1197100}I want to take care of the puppy!\NGo, liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:00.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198300,1200620}I can't do that before you promise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.06,0:20:02.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201060,1202060}Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:06.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205000,1206290}Oh! John!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:12.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210980,1212780}I can't leave you now, grab it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:18.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213730,1218530}No, I won't do that before you promise me\Nto take good care of Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.59,0:20:21.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219590,1221460}This time is not appropriate for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:24.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221460,1224410}I won't bother you again if you promise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:27.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225140,1227340}Insubordination will only make matters worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.34,0:20:29.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227340,1229400}Don't try to contradict me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:34.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232790,1234910}{\i1}Look, it's a ship!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:38.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236150,1238870}If you continue your stubbornness,\Nyou will regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:45.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242250,1245080}I understand, I promise you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:20:58.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258170,1258970}{\i1}Lassie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:03.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260100,1263380}This uncle lives alone, so stay with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:06.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1263400,1266120}Hm!\NAs if it would understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:08.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268030,1268900}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:10.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269140,1270540}{\i1}It's yours!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.69,0:21:14.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1270690,1274140}But I brought it to you\Nbecause you are its owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:17.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1274270,1277550}It's true that I have made you a promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:22.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277850,1282110}But if you are so proud of it\Nthen you can take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.98,0:21:26.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1282980,1286190}It's annoying, it likes you\Nso I'll leave it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:34.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1291680,1294820}Come to the hut again, all three of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.41,0:21:38.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1295410,1298940}You will taste some sea-food!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:40.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1299210,1300300}{\i1}Be sure to come!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:42.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1300300,1302880}Yes, we'll certainly come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.14,0:21:46.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1304140,1306800}Now Lassie, let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.98,0:21:49.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1306980,1309540}You'll be getting hot milk, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:00.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1319040,1320830}{\i1}Tomorrow is my mother's birthday.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.01,0:22:04.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1321010,1324450}{\i1}But my father lost his salary.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.48,0:22:07.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324480,1327280}{\i1}He can't bring any gift.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:10.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1327630,1330410}{\i1}Lassie, you'll find it with your smell!{\i0}
